flowchart LR
  RAW[Raw news JSONL: datasets/*.jsonl or data/raw/*.jsonl]
  HAVE{SFT already exists?}
  GEN[Generate SFT - OpenRouter teacher]
  SFT[SFT JSONL: data/processed/sft.jsonl]
  PREP[Chat-format and split]
  FT[LoRA SFT training - Qwen2.5 + Unsloth]
  SAVE[Save LoRA checkpoint: outputs/models/...]
  TEST[Smoke test inference]

  RAW --> HAVE
  HAVE -->|No| GEN --> SFT
  HAVE -->|Yes| SFT
  SFT --> PREP --> FT --> SAVE --> TEST
